# SPA fallback is handled by wrangler.jsonc — see
# `assets.not_found_handling: "single-page-application"`.
#
# This file exists to stop Cloudflare's Vite framework preset from
# auto-injecting `/* /index.html 200`, which Workers Static Assets
# rejects as a redirect loop (it auto-strips `.html` / `/index` and
# re-matches the wildcard).
